quran[32]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,55,"Ee qofkii rabaa ha ku waano qaato."
  74,56,"Ma waantoobayaanse in Alle doono maahee; waa Isaga Rabbiga mudan inay aadmigu ka cabsadaan, oo mudan inuu Denbi Dhaafo."
  77,43,"Cuna oo cabba si raaxo leh waa waxaad camalsan fali jirteen darteed."
  77,44,"Sidaasaan u abaal marinnaa sama falayaasha."
  77,45,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  78,40,"Waxaanu idiinka dignay cadaab dhow - Maalinka uu qofku arki waxay gacmihiisu hormarsadeen (oo khayr ah ama shar), oo gaalku odhan:Hoogaye! Maan ciid ahaado."
  79,34,"Markase ay timaaddo musiibada weyni."
  79,35,"Maalinka uu Aadmigu xusuusan wuxuu falay oo dhan."
  79,36,"Oo Naarta loo muujiyo qof (waliba) oo arkaya,"
  80,31,"Iyo midho iyo caws."
  80,32,"Sahay aad leedihiin idinka iyo xoolihiinnuba."
  80,33,"Markase ay qeylada dhego beelisada ah timaaddo (afuufka labaad ee Buunka)."
  81,28,"Qofkii idinka mid ah ee dooni inuu (ku) toosnaado (Xaqa)."
  81,29,"Oo waxna ma dooni kartaan aan ahayn wuxuu Alle doono, Rabbiga uumanka."
  83,19,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxa uu Cilliyiin yahay?"
  83,20,"Waa (aayaha mu'miniinta) kitaab (ku) calaameysan."
  83,21,"Waxaa arka (malaa’igtaa) ku dhow (Alle)."
  84,16,"Mayee, Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay cir gaduudda gabbal dhac;"
  84,17,"Iyo habeenka iyo wuxuu qariyo;"
  84,18,"Iyo dayaxa markuu buuxsamo."
  85,13,"(Alle) Isagaa uumay (uunka) dibna u soo nooleyn (dhimasho kaddib)."
  85,14,"Waa Denbi Dhaaf Badanaha, Jecel (kuwa adeeca)."
  85,15,"Rabbiga Carshiga Sharafta Badan."
  86,7,"Oo ka yimaada dhabarka iyo feeraha dhexdood,"
  86,8,"Hubaal (Alle) wuu Karaa inuu u soo celiyo nolosha (dhimasho kaddib)."
  86,9,"Maalinta waxyaalaha qarsoon iyo siraha la soo bandhigi (xaqiiqdooda)."
  87,4,"Oo ah Kan soo saara daaqa."
  87,5,"Ka dhiga markaas kaddib caws engagan oo madow."
  87,6,"Waxaan kuu akhriyeynaa (Nabiyow) Qur’aanka mana illaaweysid,"
  88,1,"Mawuusan kuu iman warka dabooshada (Qiyaamada)."
  88,2,"Wejiyaal maalintaas waxay ahaan kuwo dullaysan (waa gaalada)."
  88,3,"(Ku) howlan (shaqo dhib leh adduunka caabuddaada cid kale la jirka Alle), taag daran (Aakhirada, dulli daboolayo)."